reviews.review_text: AMAZING AMAZING and out of this world sound on this one. Great job by all the band the taper and of course us in attendance. We add to the flow and sound at every show. 1st Half step Franklins in Bay Area in years.

On the day that I was born... A very rockin 2nd set. With all the great early stuff available at the Archive I have to remember to check out shows from my own era.
Half Step>Franklins>Playing>China Doll>Playin!
And really this is mighty fine.

Try to read between the lines Nice SBD for 86'..Love the Iko Iko to start and set the pace for a real good show..I love the placement of the Bertha>Sat Night to end 1st set~! You would need a break after that combo..Real nice 1/2 Step>Franklins to open 2nd set with a sweet China Doll>Playin' jam before Drumz..Give it a Whirl~Forever Grateful>Forever Dead
